<td tEditID="c1r1" style=" background-color:#FFFFFF; bEditID:r3st1; color:#000000; bLabel:main; font-size:12pt; font-family:arial;" aEditID="c1r1" locked="1" >
<![CDATA[<p class="MsoNormal" style="font-size: 12pt;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 17.12px; background: white;">Hi {!Lead.FirstName},<br></span><br></font></p><p class="MsoNormal"><font face="Arial, sans-serif">Having come across your business, I believe our business insurance may be of interest to you as we offer coverage tailored specifically to your industry.&nbsp;<br></font><br><font face="Arial, sans-serif">Here at Kingsbridge, we offer a complete package of cover that is designed specifically for UK businesses.&nbsp;<br></font><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font><font face="arial">I am confident I can provide you with a competitive quote in 5-10 minutes.&nbsp;</font><b style="font-size: 12pt;">Not ready for a quote yet?</b><font face="arial" style="font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp;</font><a href="https://calendly.com/d/cm3g-k74-js2/kingsbridge-insurance-call-back" style="font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><b>Book a call with me</b></a><font face="arial" style="font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp;closer to your renewal date.<br></font><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><font face="arial"><br></font><b style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">Plus, if you book a call with me,</b></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><b>&nbsp;I can provide you with an additional welcome discount.&nbsp;<br></b></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><b><br></b>Alternatively, you can reply to let me know a good time to call or contact me on&nbsp;</span><b style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">01242 807223</b><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">. Our office is open between the hours of 8:00am-5:30pm, Monday-Friday.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">&nbsp;<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><br>I look forward to hearing from you.&nbsp;<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><br>Kind regards,<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><br>{!User.FirstName}&nbsp;<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Sales Team<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><br>E: salesteam@kingsbridge.co.uk<br></span><font style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">T:&nbsp;</font><font style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">01242 808740</font></p>]]></td>
